# Stage 4: First Revelation - Begin
# Midnight meeting at the museum

label stage4_begin:
    scene bg library with fade

    "Midnight. The museum entrance feels ominous in the darkness."

    show s at center with dissolve

    s "You came. Good."

    show h at left with dissolve
    show l at right with dissolve

    h "Professor, what is this about?"
    l "And why here, at this hour?"

    s "Because this is where it began. And where it must end."

    jump stage4_artifact_history
